  "body": "<!-- **Are you in the right place?**\r\n1. For issues or feature requests, please create an issue in this repository.\r\n2. For general technical and non-technical questions, we are happy to help you on our [Rook.io Slack](https://slack.rook.io/).\r\n3. Did you already search the existing open issues for anything similar? -->\r\n\r\n**Is this a bug report or feature request?**\r\n* Feature Request\r\n\r\n**What should the feature do:**\r\nNot really a feature more a refacto that can be extend to a feature if we enforce the pod anti affinity to the mds component.\r\nWith PR #4457 4457 the mon setPodPlacement method has been partially duplicated to manage pod anti affinity on gateways\r\nWe must refactor this to one generic method used by those 2 components and that can be used by other (like the MDS)\r\n\r\n**What is use case behind this feature:**\r\nSimplify the code and testing.\r\nOther component can used it if needed without duplicating the code again\r\n\r\n**Environment**:\r\n<!-- Specific environment information that helps with the feature request -->\r\n",
